        </a>
        
        <a href="/case-types/lyft-distracted-driver/" class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-xl hover:shadow-lg transition">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-3">üì±</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Distracted Driving</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Accidents caused by Lyft app distraction</p>
        </a>
        
        <a href="/case-types/lyft-wrongful-death/" class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-xl hover:shadow-lg transition">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-3">üíî</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Wrongful Death</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Fatal Lyft accident claims</p>
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-8 text-center">
        <a href="/case-types/" class="text-secondary font-semibold hover:underline">
          View all case types ‚Üí
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Lyft Accident FAQs</h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <details class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow group">
          <summary class="font-bold text-lg cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            Who is liable when a Lyft driver causes an accident?
            <span class="text-secondary group-open:rotate-180 transition">‚ñº</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
            Liability depends on the driver's status at the time of the accident. When a passenger is in the vehicle or the driver is en route to a pickup, Lyft's $1 million commercial insurance typically covers the accident. Both the driver and Lyft may be held liable depending on the circumstances.
          </p>
        </details>
        
        <details class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow group">
          <summary class="font-bold text-lg cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            How much is my Lyft accident claim worth?
            <span class="text-secondary group-open:rotate-180 transition">‚ñº</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
            Settlement values vary widely based on injury severity, medical expenses, lost wages, pain and suffering, and other factors. Minor injury claims may settle for $10,000-$50,000, while serious injury cases can reach $500,000 or more. Fatal Lyft accident claims may exceed $1 million.
          </p>
        </details>
        
        <details class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow group">
          <summary class="font-bold text-lg cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            Is Lyft insurance different from Lyft's?
            <span class="text-secondary group-open:rotate-180 transition">‚ñº</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
            Both companies provide similar $1 million liability coverage during active rides. However, Lyft has historically offered uninsured motorist coverage in Period 1 (app on, waiting for requests), while Lyft only provides this in Periods 2 and 3. The claims process and insurance carriers may also differ.
          </p>
        </details>
        
        <details class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow group">
          <summary class="font-bold text-lg cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            How do I report a Lyft accident?
            <span class="text-secondary group-open:rotate-180 transition">‚ñº</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
            You can report an accident through the Lyft app's Help section, call 911 for emergencies, and file a police report. For injury claims, contact Lyft's insurance carrier directly. We recommend consulting with an attorney before speaking to any insurance adjusters.
          </p>
        </details>
        
        <details class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow group">
          <summary class="font-bold text-lg cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            Do I need a lawyer for a Lyft accident claim?
            <span class="text-secondary group-open:rotate-180 transition">‚ñº</span>
